      <arrangement id="aspace_5a530db3d1e436a69612231a92919266">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged in five series and one addition: I. Correspondence and Lectures. II. Research Materials. III. Writings. IV. Writings of Others and Miscellaneous. V. Papers Re: Books and Bibliography.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <bioghist id="aspace_27a4dca129ee7ba075287835f37be640">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Samuel C. Harvey (1886-1953): surgeon; Ph.B., Yale, 1907, M.D., 1911; instructor of surgery, Yale University, 1919-1921, associate professor, 1921-1924, William H. Carmalt professor of surgery, 1924-1947, professor of surgery (oncology), 1947-1952; retired and continued research in field.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_804a653c9929d3eb3c793f47d669a451">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Personal and professional papers of Samuel Clark Harvey.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
